{"tid":1753753,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"其實民主派點解唔可以搞民間初選","createTime":"2019-11-25T04:23:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-25T07:05:50.000Z","uid":165336,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"38905d25cd16b9f155a13bba737695667f469cf0","tid":1753753,"uid":165336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T04:23:09.000Z","msg":"西貢區 環保北 自己友互介輸咗<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1752592\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1752592</a><br />\n<br />\n睇見就火滾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />下次可唔可以網上搞次投票俾泛民/本土初選<br />\n輸果個自己退選<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa63b6630b3a68357d599d737d86f0dc68411baf","tid":1753753,"uid":8441,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T04:34:07.000Z","msg":"政治潔辟，free will<br />\n<br />\n但其實美帝都有黨初選"},{"pid":"3f9c533d7c05b952df781132609d82f6bcd5905f","tid":1753753,"uid":165336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T05:29:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"432b16f005b6735e1a5406f3ee8a190cc231030c","tid":1753753,"uid":258696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T05:30:06.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">咪撚做休息撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n投完票，贏輸都好，我地有新野做。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">文宣方向：</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">1. 有得一人一票，社會氣氛好左幾多？而且大家都相信投票，年青人到長者教出黎投，所以應該一人一票選特首。<br />\n<br />\n2.我地要將種票、票多過投票人、送禮各種唔公平現象比英美兩國知。<br />\n<br />\n3. Poly手足被困多日，要求警察撤退。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;